{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01FUDJjWLcnwiWHbAvvMDoX1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"```\n[OK] Session retrospective complete\n```\n\n**Session summary:** This was no-op session #36. Stories 16-7 and 16-8 were already verified and committed as `done` in prior sessions, but ralph's state regeneration keeps reverting `sprint-state.json`, causing the orchestrator to re-detect and restore the correct statuses each loop.\n\n**Root cause:** Ralph lacks a monotonic status guard — it overwrites `sprint-state.json` without checking whether the committed version has higher-status values.\n\n**Critical action items:**\n1. **Fix now:** Add monotonic status guard to ralph — never regress a story from `done` to a lower status\n2. **Fix now:** Add sprint-complete early exit — when all stories are `done`, ralph should stop spawning new sessions entirely\n\nThese two fixes would have prevented ~36 no-op sessions and an estimated $144-180 in wasted API spend. Total sprint cost is now $887 across 6,469 API calls."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1572,"cache_read_input_tokens":45962,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1572},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7ea5f697-8411-4b70-a21e-041b4c52ed05","uuid":"de1db006-f272-4ef0-806e-c8f5609f2512"}
