{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":250313,"duration_api_ms":241106,"num_turns":17,"result":"```\n[OK] Session retrospective complete\n```\n\n**Session summary:** This was no-op session #36. Stories 16-7 and 16-8 were already verified and committed as `done` in prior sessions, but ralph's state regeneration keeps reverting `sprint-state.json`, causing the orchestrator to re-detect and restore the correct statuses each loop.\n\n**Root cause:** Ralph lacks a monotonic status guard — it overwrites `sprint-state.json` without checking whether the committed version has higher-status values.\n\n**Critical action items:**\n1. **Fix now:** Add monotonic status guard to ralph — never regress a story from `done` to a lower status\n2. **Fix now:** Add sprint-complete early exit — when all stories are `done`, ralph should stop spawning new sessions entirely\n\nThese two fixes would have prevented ~36 no-op sessions and an estimated $144-180 in wasted API spend. Total sprint cost is now $887 across 6,469 API calls.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"7ea5f697-8411-4b70-a21e-041b4c52ed05","total_cost_usd":1.2138307499999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":16,"cache_creation_input_tokens":50588,"cache_read_input_tokens":494296,"output_tokens":5725,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":50588,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":25,"outputTokens":10290,"cacheReadInputTokens":726224,"cacheCreationInputTokens":94935,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.2138307499999998,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"be523ac3-b2c9-4d84-8278-f4a95070982b"}
